sTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530991\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pod1665702963880.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pod1665702963880.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pod1665702963880.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pod1665702963880\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Configuring SYB for Unicode\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">To configure the Sybase connector to use Unicode, edit the application assignment file.\n </p>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step\" id=\"pod1665702963880__li_d26441e1_d26442e1_d26443e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">To enable Unicode support in the Sybase connector:\n </span>\n<ol class=\"ol substeps\" type=\"a\">\n<li class=\"li substep\" id=\"pod1665702963880__li_d26444e1_d26445e1_d26446e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Specify the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">unicode</span> connector option.\n </span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li substep\" id=\"pod1665702963880__li_d26447e1_d26448e1_d26449e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">To enable storage of the entire Unicode range (or SMP) in W packing code fields, also set the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">smp</span> option.\n </span>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"pod1665702963880__li_d26450e1_d26451e1_d26452e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">To enable Unicode support in the SQL workbench, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sql</span> ProcScript statement, and error messages, specify the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">keyword</span> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">charset utf 8</code> options.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"pod1665702963880__li_d26453e1_d26454e1_d26455e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">To enable support for service stored procedures, ensure that the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$DEF_CHARSET</span> is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">UTF8</code>.\n </span>\n</li></ol></section>\n<section class=\"section result body required-cleanup-multiple-ol-elements-in-topic-body\" id=\"pod1665702963880__result_w3752ab1b5b3_w3753ab1b5_w3754ab1\">\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p exampletitle\" id=\"pod1665702963880__p_d59003e1_d59004e1_d59005e1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Example: Unicode\n                  Configuration</strong>\n</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[SETTINGS]\n$DEF_CHARSET = UTF8\n[DRIVER_SETTINGS]\nusys$syb_params charset utf8 ,unicode, smp, keyword</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/udi1665702731005.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Unicode</a><p>Unicode is an industry standard designed to allow text and symbols from all languages to be consistently represented and manipulated by computers.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bgx1665702950736.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>unicode</a><p>Enable or disable Unicode support in the MQL connector.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ozf1665702734970.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>keyword</a><p>Adds double quotes around field and table names and sets the Sybase option quoted_identifier on.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tke1665702734474.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>charset</a><p>Set default character set used by the Sybase open client.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/azs1665703222737.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$DEF_CHARSET</a><p>Specify the default character set used for storing data in String fields with C packing code.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530991\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530991\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Configuring SYB for Unicode Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Configuring SYB for Unicode To configure the Sybase connector to use Unicode, edit the application assignment file. To enable Unicode support in the Sybase connector: Specify the unicode connector option. To enable storage of the entire Unicode range (or SMP) in W packing code fields, also set the smp option. To enable Unicode support in the SQL workbench, sql ProcScript statement, and error messages, specify the keyword and charset utf 8 options. To enable support for service stored procedures, ensure that the $DEF_CHARSET is set to UTF8 . Example: Unicode Configuration [SETTINGS] $DEF_CHARSET = UTF8 [DRIVER_SETTINGS] usys$syb_params charset utf8 ,unicode, smp, keyword Copy Related Links Unicode Unicode is an industry standard designed to allow text and symbols from all languages to be consistently represented and manipulated by computers. unicode Enable or disable Unicode support in the MQL connector. keyword Adds double quotes around field and table names and sets the Sybase option quoted_identifier on. charset Set default character set used by the Sybase open client. $DEF_CHARSET Specify the default character set used for storing data in String fields with C packing code. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}